WEBVTT

01:38.080 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 7

02:06.920 --> 02:10.080
You're amazing!
You kill without spilling blood.

02:10.520 --> 02:14.840
You're too kind. Come on, let's go
take on the last level of Condor Heroes.

02:18.320 --> 02:19.160
Wait.

02:21.680 --> 02:24.200
Did you say you're at the last level
of in-game couple's quests?

02:25.160 --> 02:26.000
That's right.

02:28.640 --> 02:30.280
You mean the extremely difficult one?

02:30.920 --> 02:31.880
The one level that to this day

02:32.280 --> 02:34.480
no in-game couple across all servers
has ever accomplished?

02:36.040 --> 02:37.200
I think so.

02:37.280 --> 02:39.960
Darn! Only an extreme player like Nai

02:40.040 --> 02:42.040
can accomplish such a difficult quest.

02:43.560 --> 02:44.640
You guys could never do it.

02:45.080 --> 02:47.080
Of course, not. We're not that extreme.

02:48.160 --> 02:49.960
That's not the point.

02:50.400 --> 02:53.480
First of all, you need to have
an in-game spouse.

02:53.840 --> 02:54.880
What?

02:57.960 --> 02:58.920
Let's go.

03:13.760 --> 03:15.760
Yixiao Naihe, Luwei Weiwei,

03:16.520 --> 03:18.200
what a compatible in-game couple.

03:19.000 --> 03:20.320
Your love and courage

03:20.800 --> 03:23.840
have helped you overcome
various obstacles and reach here.

03:24.480 --> 03:26.600
First of all, congratulations.

03:27.000 --> 03:30.120
Now, it's the last level of Condor Heroes.

03:30.200 --> 03:33.640
Yearning Formation is the most difficult,
ultimate challenge.

03:34.160 --> 03:37.800
Are you confident you will be the first
in-game couple of all servers to crack it?

03:43.520 --> 03:44.760
ACCEPT QUEST

03:52.560 --> 03:55.720
Congratulations for arriving
at the last level of Condor Heroes.

03:55.800 --> 03:58.880
Your in-game spouse must find you
within 16 hours.

03:58.960 --> 04:02.400
If he cannot find you, you'll fail
the Condor Heroes quest.

04:03.760 --> 04:07.760
16 hours? How hard is this quest?

04:08.080 --> 04:12.240
Does it mean we can't log off?
Let me search the forum.

04:12.680 --> 04:16.120
I fell down from up high.
Could I be at the bottom of a cliff?

04:17.000 --> 04:20.519
Does that mean Naihe needs to jump off
a cliff to find me?

04:33.800 --> 04:39.120
I knew it!
This place isn't even on the map.

04:40.640 --> 04:41.560
Weiwei?

04:47.720 --> 04:50.840
Naihe? We can still chat?

04:52.600 --> 04:55.960
I was just informed that my quest
is to find you in 16 hours.

04:56.040 --> 04:57.920
How are your surroundings?

04:58.400 --> 04:59.280
I...

05:01.160 --> 05:07.760
My surroundings are very dark, very dark.

05:09.640 --> 05:11.120
You can't see anything?

05:12.400 --> 05:13.360
No.

05:19.520 --> 05:20.600
What about sound?

05:28.120 --> 05:31.120
I seem to hear water.

05:37.560 --> 05:38.480
I see.

05:44.560 --> 05:46.440
I can't just twiddle my thumbs.

05:49.840 --> 05:55.600
If we can still chat,
why don't I find some information for him?

06:28.800 --> 06:30.280
Could she be nearby?

06:40.480 --> 06:41.400
Naihe!

06:44.320 --> 06:45.280
What's up?

06:46.720 --> 06:50.040
It's so sick! I checked
the official website for this quest.

06:50.120 --> 06:51.640
It doesn't offer a player's guide.

06:51.720 --> 06:54.600
Not only that, there's only
a one-line description for this level.

06:56.160 --> 06:57.200
What is it?

07:01.560 --> 07:04.440
In-game couple needs telepathic connection
to crack this level.

07:04.520 --> 07:05.960
What the heck is that?

07:39.480 --> 07:43.120
It's so dark, it's almost like a blackout.

07:44.120 --> 07:45.920
I think I'll study for now.

07:54.960 --> 07:58.120
Do you know how much I miss you?

07:58.560 --> 08:02.120
I miss you as much
as the red dots are deeply set on a die.

08:04.160 --> 08:08.040
I've been waiting here for 30 years.

08:08.480 --> 08:10.440
You're the first to show up on this cliff.

08:11.600 --> 08:14.240
30 years ago, my junior fellow apprentice
disappeared without warning.

08:14.920 --> 08:19.160
I tracked him to this place,
but I've been held up by this game of go.

08:20.040 --> 08:22.680
The clues are likely on the board,

08:23.840 --> 08:27.040
but I'm no expert at go.

08:28.200 --> 08:31.040
Young man, can you help me
solve this riddle?

09:05.720 --> 09:07.120
I had no idea!

09:11.480 --> 09:17.000
If you see my junior fellow apprentice
beyond this natural moat,

09:20.080 --> 09:23.320
please give him this jade pendant.

09:27.280 --> 09:30.760
But a Yearning Formation lies
beyond this natural moat.

09:30.840 --> 09:35.000
I hear it is extremely indomitable,
you must be extra cautious.

09:36.640 --> 09:41.000
I have a secret manuscript for
overcoming the level, please take a look.

09:48.560 --> 09:50.600
This way, please.

11:42.200 --> 11:47.560
All love and relationships
are unpredictable and ephemeral.

11:47.640 --> 11:51.640
Love and care for loved ones spark worry;
love and care for loved ones spark fear.

11:51.720 --> 11:55.080
Freedom from love
is freedom from worry and fear.

11:55.560 --> 11:59.320
I've waited for 30 years.
I'm surprised to see anyone make it here.

11:59.400 --> 12:04.040
However, in order to rescue your lover,
you must get through me first.

12:05.320 --> 12:09.720
Are you willing to sacrifice everything
to rescue your lover?

12:11.240 --> 12:12.160
WILL YOU TAKE ON
THE OWNER OF HAPPY COUPLE?

12:12.240 --> 12:13.160
YOUR CULTIVATED STATUS WILL DISSIPATE
AND YOU MUST REINCARNATE, SHOULD YOU FAIL.

12:44.440 --> 12:47.760
You can still leave, before I begin.

13:14.120 --> 13:15.720
What's that on your waist?

13:19.680 --> 13:21.600
So he has searched for me!

13:22.240 --> 13:24.800
Brother, I misjudged you.

13:26.680 --> 13:29.520
Young man, your in-game spouse
is at the bottom of the valley.

13:30.520 --> 13:32.600
Let Happy Couple take you there.

13:33.200 --> 13:35.920
These two phoenixes
have kept me company for 30 years.

13:36.560 --> 13:41.200
I gift them to you now.
May destiny bring the lovers together.

13:58.360 --> 14:00.000
Your husband Yixiao Naihe

14:00.080 --> 14:03.480
has passed the test of Yearning Formation,
the last level.

14:03.560 --> 14:06.600
Congratulations on accomplishing
the quest of Condor Heroes.

14:14.720 --> 14:17.840
It's so crazy how Naihe arrives
surrounded by a thousand beams of light.

14:17.920 --> 14:20.920
He's two wings
shy of an angelic appearance.

14:26.760 --> 14:27.600
You found me.

14:29.240 --> 14:30.320
Sorry to have kept you waiting.

14:39.360 --> 14:41.160
Yixiao Naihe and Luwei Weiwei

14:41.240 --> 14:44.160
accomplished Condor Heroes,
the ultimate in-game couple's quest.

14:44.280 --> 14:46.200
They receive 10 million experience points,

14:46.280 --> 14:48.720
the title of Top Golden Couple
of "A Chinese Ghost Story,"

14:48.800 --> 14:52.080
along with the first-ever
couple's flying steeds,

14:52.160 --> 14:53.720
Happy Couple.

14:54.080 --> 14:56.160
Darn! Couple's flying steeds?

14:56.560 --> 14:58.280
"A Chinese Ghost Story"
has couple's flying steeds now?

14:59.280 --> 15:00.800
That can't be the only pair, right?

15:00.880 --> 15:04.320
Is "A Chinese Ghost Story" going to launch
a couple's flying steeds function?

15:04.400 --> 15:08.520
Definitely! They can't be the only pair.
How else will the game make money?

15:13.360 --> 15:17.400
So, they're Happy Couple?
They look a little fat, though.

15:17.480 --> 15:18.320
Can they really fly?

15:27.320 --> 15:29.240
Come, let's go for a ride.

15:31.200 --> 15:32.240
I realize that

15:32.320 --> 15:34.200
Luwei Weiwei always strikes a win,

15:34.280 --> 15:35.640
just when you think she's hit rock bottom.

15:35.720 --> 15:38.680
I know! When she and Zhenshui Wuxiang
annulled their in-game marriage,

15:38.760 --> 15:40.400
I thought she got dumped.

15:40.480 --> 15:43.280
Then she turns around and couples up
with Yixiao Naihe.

15:43.600 --> 15:44.680
Amazing!

15:45.120 --> 15:47.760
Maybe Zhenshui Wuxiang was the one
who got dumped?

15:49.480 --> 15:51.000
How did you find me?

15:51.680 --> 15:53.200
There were clues, actually.

15:54.960 --> 15:58.360
Is Yearning Formation the legendary
Qimen Five-Element Array?

15:58.440 --> 15:59.560
It's not that deep.

16:00.160 --> 16:02.480
Before I started,
an NPC gave me directions.

16:02.560 --> 16:06.160
About 2,000 words of clues in ten seconds.

16:07.800 --> 16:11.400
You memorized those clues in ten seconds?

16:11.880 --> 16:13.360
You're inhuman!

16:13.440 --> 16:15.360
Nobody can read that fast!

16:17.400 --> 16:18.680
I screen-grabbed.

16:20.920 --> 16:25.200
That's right! You can screen-grab!
Only a dummy would try to memorize it.

16:25.720 --> 16:28.200
I'm so silly! Why didn't I think of that?

16:29.080 --> 16:31.120
But you're incredible
for thinking on your feet,

16:31.200 --> 16:33.440
to decide to screen-grab in no time.

16:36.920 --> 16:38.000
You quit the clan?

16:41.360 --> 16:42.840
A few days ago.

16:46.040 --> 16:49.120
Luwei Weiwei, your team stole
Xiaoyu Qingqing's prey.

16:50.160 --> 16:52.720
You're in the same clan.
That's uncalled for.

16:53.160 --> 16:54.520
Don't you owe me an explanation?

16:55.120 --> 16:57.800
Since when is Xiaoyu Qingqing in our clan?

17:01.160 --> 17:04.119
Clan Leader took in the Xiaoyus,
for Zhenshui and Yaoyao's sake.

17:04.640 --> 17:06.680
But Xiaoyu Qingqing
is particularly annoying.

17:06.920 --> 17:09.760
She's always flirting
with the guys in the clan.

17:09.960 --> 17:11.280
She even got to Clan Leader.

17:12.280 --> 17:14.680
I saw the two of them alone several times,

17:15.040 --> 17:16.800
even riding a horse together.

17:20.319 --> 17:23.040
Clan Leader Zhan,
why don't you ask Xiaoyu Qingqing

17:23.119 --> 17:25.520
what's going on?
She'd better give me an explanation.

17:27.200 --> 17:28.359
What's the meaning of this, Luwei?

17:28.800 --> 17:30.680
I know you have issues
with Xiaoyu Qingqing,

17:30.960 --> 17:32.840
but I hope you can focus on
the topic at hand.

17:33.960 --> 17:35.920
How am I not focusing on
the topic at hand?

17:36.240 --> 17:37.280
Hey...

17:41.080 --> 17:43.440
Xiaoyu Qingqing, please come out.

17:43.520 --> 17:46.400
Tell Clan Leader Zhan
what happened exactly.

17:48.080 --> 17:49.960
Xiaoyu Qingqing, come out, now!

17:52.440 --> 17:55.960
If you won't talk, Xiaoyu Qingqing,
I'll ask in the public chat room.

17:56.600 --> 17:58.120
There were several teams present.

17:58.200 --> 18:01.040
I'm sure someone will explain
what happened then.

18:04.760 --> 18:06.520
I was out. What's going on?

18:08.200 --> 18:11.600
Playing dumb?
The chat record is very clear.

18:17.000 --> 18:21.200
You mean that thing?
I said I failed to steal a prey.

18:21.280 --> 18:24.400
I said you stole the prey.
Did I say something wrong?

18:25.160 --> 18:27.280
I didn't know Tianxia would misread that
and ask you about it.

18:28.440 --> 18:29.680
What you're saying is,

18:29.760 --> 18:32.120
Clan Leader Zhan purposely
twisted your words to slander me?

18:35.160 --> 18:37.800
Clan Leader Zhan,
you owe me an explanation.

18:37.880 --> 18:39.000
It feels awful to be wrongly accused.

18:43.080 --> 18:44.960
Xiaoyu Qingqing is trying to use him
to get to you.

18:45.960 --> 18:48.520
Then she's not doing a good job at it.

18:51.400 --> 18:54.520
I was mistaken.
I'm glad it's just a misunderstanding.

18:55.280 --> 18:56.880
Team spirit is imperative to the clan.

18:58.080 --> 19:00.160
But you should be mindful of something,
Luwei Weiwei.

19:01.280 --> 19:02.680
What is it? I'm all ears.

19:03.560 --> 19:06.200
When Zhenshui and Yaoyao got married,

19:06.600 --> 19:08.760
the medicine you sold
on Red Sparrow Bridge

19:09.360 --> 19:11.440
was made with materials
from the clan, right?

19:12.080 --> 19:14.200
You shouldn't have sold it on your own.

19:14.280 --> 19:18.320
It's fine, because you only did it once.
Just don't do it again.

19:20.160 --> 19:22.200
Clan Leader Zhan remembers something
that happened so long ago.

19:23.360 --> 19:25.000
If I remember correctly,

19:25.080 --> 19:28.680
the so-called materials from
the clan warehouse were herbs I collected.

19:29.440 --> 19:32.480
You have a problem with me selling
medicine made from the herbs I collected?

19:33.640 --> 19:36.320
- Wait, Luwei, you're being--
- Enough.

19:36.560 --> 19:39.280
We're all in the same clan.
We shouldn't fight.

19:39.360 --> 19:41.640
- Yes, we're in the same clan.
- That's right.

19:41.720 --> 19:43.080
Forget it.

19:45.440 --> 19:49.040
Xiaoyu Qingqing, you and I both know
what took place exactly.

19:50.280 --> 19:51.800
You either apologize to me now,

19:52.320 --> 19:54.760
or never let me catch you
killing a monster again.

19:55.680 --> 19:58.400
Otherwise, I will make
your false accusation come true.

19:59.880 --> 20:02.960
Luwei Weiwei, you're such a bully!

20:03.480 --> 20:04.920
Why blow things out of proportion?

20:05.000 --> 20:07.240
So what if you've got a high grade?
She said it's a misunderstanding.

20:07.320 --> 20:08.520
Why can't you live and let live?

20:13.720 --> 20:16.840
Tianxia, I didn't mean to do that.
Why is she so mean?

20:20.760 --> 20:24.360
This is no longer
the Bihai Chaosheng House I know.

20:24.840 --> 20:26.880
Weiwei, don't be rash.

20:31.720 --> 20:33.960
I've said all that's needed to be said.

20:35.680 --> 20:41.440
Comrades, we'll still be friends,
when we meet in this world.

20:43.880 --> 20:46.920
Luwei Weiwei quits the clan.

20:49.040 --> 20:50.600
- What...
- What's going on?

20:51.840 --> 20:52.840
That's too much!

21:00.040 --> 21:01.880
All good things come to an end.

21:01.960 --> 21:04.920
Luwei Weiwei quits Bihai Chaosheng House.

21:08.440 --> 21:09.760
- That's too much!
- Right?

21:09.840 --> 21:11.200
- How can she do this?
- How can this be?

21:11.280 --> 21:13.600
- Right?
- It's quite a shame.

21:19.840 --> 21:22.680
That's good.
From now on, we'll be together.

21:25.360 --> 21:29.320
We'll brave this world together,
like a pair of wild mandarin ducks.

21:30.040 --> 21:34.320
Wild mandarin ducks?
I remember we were formally married.

21:37.600 --> 21:39.000
You have no sense of humor.

21:40.000 --> 21:41.560
Marital status is important.

21:56.560 --> 22:01.600
Fine, Naihe does have a sense of humor.
He's just a bit a stoic.

22:08.640 --> 22:10.800
It may be familiar scenery,

22:11.400 --> 22:15.360
but you still get different feelings,
despite looking at it every day.

22:16.000 --> 22:17.480
Like now.

22:20.760 --> 22:21.600
A new name?

22:42.280 --> 22:46.040
Weiwei, this facial mask is pretty good.

22:47.720 --> 22:49.080
Weiwei?

22:49.560 --> 22:50.760
I heard you.

22:51.600 --> 22:56.840
Don't tell me
you're doing that in the game world?

22:57.240 --> 23:01.280
Don't worry. I've finished my homework
and edited my thesis.

23:01.640 --> 23:03.920
- My exams won't be affected.
- Who's worried about your exams?

23:04.000 --> 23:05.720
Who's worried about your homework?

23:05.800 --> 23:09.160
I'm just worried you'd get conned!

23:14.120 --> 23:15.680
Bei Weiwei,

23:16.480 --> 23:21.960
don't you think you look like
you're totally in love?

23:23.560 --> 23:25.560
- Just go use your facial mask.
- That's what I'm doing.

23:36.880 --> 23:37.800
Yu!

23:38.800 --> 23:40.880
Mr. Li. So sorry.

23:40.960 --> 23:43.280
The traffic in Capital City is terrible.

23:43.360 --> 23:45.680
I took a cab
and the driver was so grumpy.

23:45.760 --> 23:49.240
It's fine. I just got here, too.
Sit. What would you like a drink?

23:49.320 --> 23:51.520
- Anything's fine.
- Sure. Waiter!

23:52.440 --> 23:55.720
You took a cab here, Yu?

23:55.800 --> 23:58.280
Yes, that's why I was late.

23:59.840 --> 24:03.480
A talent like you
shouldn't live like that.

24:04.320 --> 24:06.160
Our company's key tech guys

24:06.400 --> 24:09.840
each have a company car
and housing reimbursement.

24:10.200 --> 24:11.920
Really? Such great benefits!

24:12.600 --> 24:14.920
Talents should be treated well.

24:16.000 --> 24:19.320
A key tech guy who joined us
the year before last

24:19.560 --> 24:21.520
bought a house this year.

24:22.640 --> 24:23.920
He's even bought a house?

24:24.080 --> 24:27.400
You should know,
our company's employee benefits

24:27.480 --> 24:29.000
are the best in the industry.

24:30.800 --> 24:34.000
Yu, let's be frank today.

24:34.080 --> 24:35.560
I won't beat around the bush.

24:36.000 --> 24:37.960
Ever since we met last time,

24:38.040 --> 24:39.840
we've been particularly taken with you.

24:40.400 --> 24:43.840
What do you say?
Are you interested in joining our team?

24:47.360 --> 24:50.520
It's quite tempting, Mr. Li,

24:50.960 --> 24:53.480
but I'm very attached to our work.

24:54.200 --> 24:56.640
Why don't we wait
until the game is launched?

24:56.720 --> 24:58.520
It makes more sense for me
to join you after.

25:03.200 --> 25:06.120
Yu, you're too inflexible.

25:06.880 --> 25:10.520
Why don't you develop the game
in collaboration with us?

25:10.600 --> 25:12.960
We really love your idea.

25:13.040 --> 25:14.560
If we play our cards right,

25:14.640 --> 25:18.640
we'll surely be able to create a legend
of 100 million in monthly revenue.

25:19.360 --> 25:22.040
But, it's Mr. Xiao's work.

25:23.120 --> 25:27.160
I think a huge part of it
is the result of your labor.

25:28.600 --> 25:33.520
Mr. Li, Mr. Xiao and I are students
who share the same dorm.

25:33.720 --> 25:38.760
That's right, he's your fellow student.
Why are you willing to live in his shadow?

25:39.280 --> 25:42.560
What's more, from what I can see,
you're just as capable as he is.

25:43.640 --> 25:47.160
You're a young man.
You should give yourself more options,

25:47.480 --> 25:49.520
create more possibilities, right?

25:53.680 --> 25:58.000
On top of that,
you're a team of college students.

25:58.080 --> 26:00.080
You have zero experience
and social contacts.

26:01.280 --> 26:04.280
You know full well,
even without me saying,

26:04.360 --> 26:06.800
just how many obstacles
you will encounter,

26:06.880 --> 26:08.760
and how little chance you have of success.

26:09.880 --> 26:14.320
Work with us, though,
you can make miracles happen.

26:34.320 --> 26:38.160
This is just the monthly wage.
You'll get bonus, once the game is a hit.

26:38.720 --> 26:40.840
I hope you can feel

26:40.920 --> 26:44.280
the depth of sincerity I'm showing,
on behalf of our company.

26:46.760 --> 26:50.960
What? He says he needs to think about it?

26:52.000 --> 26:55.480
Time is money! We can't wait.

27:01.800 --> 27:05.280
Well, pay him another visit
in a couple of days.

27:05.720 --> 27:07.440
Raise the signing fee

27:10.000 --> 27:11.160
by 30 percent.

27:14.040 --> 27:17.760
That's right.
We must succeed in poaching him.

27:18.360 --> 27:22.400
Once he's on board,
his attitude will change.

27:22.480 --> 27:25.640
Then, his entire team
will come on board. Get it?

27:33.160 --> 27:37.600
Yiran, remember to knock
before you come in next time.

27:40.120 --> 27:44.040
Uncle, are you really going to poach
Yu Banshan and the others?

27:45.680 --> 27:47.760
I'm telling you,
you must keep it a secret.

27:48.040 --> 27:50.760
Do not tell other people
about what you just heard.

27:50.840 --> 27:52.200
Propriety is a must.

27:52.560 --> 27:53.680
Then Xiao Nai...

27:54.880 --> 27:58.160
Uncle, what you're doing is immoral.

27:59.640 --> 28:00.920
Immoral?

28:02.800 --> 28:04.440
You call that immoral?

28:05.560 --> 28:07.040
You're still young.

28:07.400 --> 28:10.720
You don't know anything about business.

28:12.720 --> 28:16.200
Those college kids think they can succeed
just by having a good idea.

28:16.680 --> 28:19.920
Take a look out there.
Failed projects are everywhere.

28:20.200 --> 28:21.680
How many have succeeded?

28:22.640 --> 28:26.160
Young people can get lost
and lose their way.

28:26.920 --> 28:28.040
When that happens,

28:28.320 --> 28:31.320
they need older folks like us
to give them pointers.

28:32.120 --> 28:34.560
So they won't waste time and money.

28:36.960 --> 28:38.360
Uncle,

28:38.440 --> 28:41.320
if you poach Yu Banshan and the others,

28:41.400 --> 28:42.680
what will happen to Xiao Nai?

28:44.760 --> 28:47.640
Once I've got his teammates,

28:48.160 --> 28:51.560
I'll give him a better offer.
Why would Xiao Nai turn me down?

28:54.320 --> 28:56.680
Don't you believe in
your uncle's capability?

28:57.160 --> 28:58.440
Don't worry over nothing.

28:58.880 --> 29:02.960
What matters the most for you right now
is to keep up your studies. Okay?

29:24.160 --> 29:27.000
Why is Yugong gone for so long?
Did he give in?

29:46.640 --> 29:47.560
Nana?

29:53.480 --> 29:58.840
So you went to the boys dorm
to try to tell Xiao Nai everything?

29:58.920 --> 29:59.920
Yes.

30:00.320 --> 30:02.640
I already saw him,

30:02.720 --> 30:06.120
but I was still unsure
if I should tell him.

30:06.880 --> 30:11.880
Thankfully you didn't, Yiran.
That's surely your intuition helping you.

30:12.360 --> 30:14.080
Are you silly or what?

30:14.360 --> 30:16.880
Whether the poaching succeeds or fails,

30:16.960 --> 30:19.640
your uncle is already the bad guy.

30:19.720 --> 30:22.640
If it fails,
we'll think of something else.

30:22.720 --> 30:24.880
If it succeeds,

30:24.960 --> 30:27.120
you'll be working
alongside Xiao Nai, no?

30:27.520 --> 30:30.800
So, I think you should take
Mr. Zhen's side.

30:31.400 --> 30:33.240
But I still think...

30:40.400 --> 30:42.120
- Why is Xiao Nai and Bei Weiwei--
- Okay.

30:42.800 --> 30:44.800
I already looked into it for you.

30:45.080 --> 30:47.440
They just happened to be sitting together.

30:47.520 --> 30:49.800
And Xiao Nai never spoke to Bei Weiwei.

30:51.400 --> 30:54.000
I'm showing you this, to tell you,

30:54.080 --> 30:55.800
opportunities are created.

30:56.240 --> 30:59.280
Opportunities won't come to you,
when you do nothing.

30:59.760 --> 31:02.440
Take Bei Weiwei, for example,
she's a computer major,

31:02.520 --> 31:05.640
yet she takes an archaeology class,
just to get to Xiao Nai.

31:05.720 --> 31:06.640
See how hard she works at it.

31:07.640 --> 31:10.480
As for you, you don't take any initiative.

31:10.560 --> 31:13.160
You think Xiao Nai will simply
fall into your lap?

31:15.320 --> 31:17.240
Anyway, I think,

31:17.960 --> 31:20.880
you have a good chance,
yet you try to destroy it.

31:20.960 --> 31:22.600
Are you silly or what?

31:25.400 --> 31:28.520
Yiran, don't go against your uncle.

31:29.960 --> 31:32.480
You should just stand with Mr. Zhen,

31:32.560 --> 31:34.840
and quietly support him.

31:35.040 --> 31:39.000
In the end, you'll still be the good guy.
Get it?

31:43.880 --> 31:47.200
I think my acting chops
are worthy of an Oscar.

31:47.280 --> 31:52.280
I vividly portrayed a college graduate's
idealism and hunger for money.

31:57.520 --> 32:02.080
It's quite tempting, Mr. Li,

32:02.160 --> 32:06.040
but I'm very attached to our work.

32:09.680 --> 32:11.200
Yu,

32:12.360 --> 32:15.240
this is just the monthly wage.

32:20.280 --> 32:22.640
You'll get a bonus once the game is a hit.

32:23.080 --> 32:24.960
I hope you can understand,

32:25.040 --> 32:30.080
I've come to you with genuine sincerity,
on behalf of our company.

32:33.120 --> 32:36.760
If I don't become a coder,
with my acting chops, I'll be an actor.

32:38.280 --> 32:40.160
They're so ruthless!

32:40.240 --> 32:42.960
They asked Yu to give them
the source code.

32:43.360 --> 32:45.640
If that happens, they can create

32:45.720 --> 32:47.800
an identical game in no time,

32:47.880 --> 32:49.600
and launch it before us.

32:49.680 --> 32:50.960
Our work would become garbage.

32:52.440 --> 32:54.680
Nai, what do we do next?

32:54.760 --> 32:56.920
You asked me to keep them hanging.

32:57.000 --> 33:01.000
Do you want me to be a spy
from within the company?

33:01.920 --> 33:05.640
Bro, you think you can be a spy,
with that IQ of yours?

33:06.080 --> 33:07.920
Don't joke around, okay?

33:08.000 --> 33:09.040
On the other hand,

33:09.400 --> 33:11.720
they might send a spy our way.

33:11.800 --> 33:13.840
What do you think, Nai?

33:14.360 --> 33:18.000
I think, they might try to box us in,

33:18.520 --> 33:20.680
and sabotage our financing opportunities.

33:25.080 --> 33:26.080
What's that?

33:27.200 --> 33:28.760
The interior of our office space.

33:29.240 --> 33:30.720
The designer just sent it over.

33:31.160 --> 33:33.800
It should be done soon.

33:35.120 --> 33:37.280
Time really does fly.

33:37.360 --> 33:39.840
We will finally have our own spot.

33:41.040 --> 33:43.480
Nai, I have no other demand.

33:43.720 --> 33:47.960
I only want a gorgeous girl
as our receptionist.

33:48.040 --> 33:49.600
- A girl.
- It can be done.

33:53.960 --> 33:54.800
That's not likely.

33:55.680 --> 33:56.880
Why's that?

33:57.320 --> 34:00.080
I just poached a master programmer,
named Ashuang.

34:00.920 --> 34:02.400
I'll introduce you soon.

34:03.400 --> 34:04.680
Wait, no...

34:05.560 --> 34:09.360
Nai. So you got a master programmer.

34:09.440 --> 34:12.520
What does that have to do with
our receptionist?

34:12.800 --> 34:13.960
He's gynophobic.

34:14.040 --> 34:16.040
What? What phobic?

34:17.480 --> 34:20.480
Mei, I'm sorry.

34:20.560 --> 34:24.199
I think I heard the word gynophobic.

34:24.560 --> 34:27.679
Looks like our company will be
another all-male joint.

34:29.360 --> 34:31.239
Oh, God!

34:31.320 --> 34:34.600
Why would a guy have such a weird problem?

34:35.280 --> 34:37.560
It's okay. Come on.

34:38.320 --> 34:40.800
There are men who don't like stinky socks.

34:40.880 --> 34:43.679
What's so odd about a guy
who doesn't like pretty ladies?

34:43.760 --> 34:44.800
Darn it!

34:45.960 --> 34:48.960
Nai, you said they would sabotage
our financing opportunities.

34:49.040 --> 34:49.880
What did you mean?

34:50.600 --> 34:54.040
They must have other tricks,
aside from poaching our team.

34:54.120 --> 34:58.600
They have more contacts in the gaming
industry. It's easy to start rumors.

35:01.400 --> 35:06.520
Mei, the world is full of malevolence.
I don't want to graduate anymore.

35:07.240 --> 35:09.640
All right. Don't be scared.

35:09.720 --> 35:13.880
You must believe, Nai trumps them
in the arena of malevolence.

35:15.960 --> 35:18.880
If we hadn't gotten in touch with them,

35:18.960 --> 35:19.800
we'd be fine.

35:20.680 --> 35:25.240
Those with treasure will inevitably meet
hungry thieves. It's unavoidable.

35:26.360 --> 35:30.160
Yes, unless we holed up
and did our own thing.

35:30.240 --> 35:32.560
But our goal isn't limited
to this mobile game.

35:34.240 --> 35:36.360
I didn't turn down Zhenyi Tech right away,

35:36.440 --> 35:37.680
because I wanted to stall for time.

35:38.400 --> 35:41.440
I never wanted to work with this company.

35:41.520 --> 35:44.840
I only went to the business meeting
to feel them out.

35:45.760 --> 35:46.640
Feel them out?

35:48.040 --> 35:50.800
The word is already out, Fengteng Tech
wants to hire an outside team

35:50.880 --> 35:53.200
to develop a new version of
"A Chinese Ghost Story."

35:53.640 --> 35:56.360
Zhenyi Tech also has big ambitions
for client-based games.

35:56.920 --> 35:58.840
They may be our biggest competition.

36:01.320 --> 36:03.680
So the mobile game meeting
was just a front?

36:05.560 --> 36:08.760
It's necessary to get to know
the character of your competitor.

36:10.960 --> 36:12.200
Hou, Mei, listen to me.

36:13.200 --> 36:15.560
We'll be fine,
as we mindlessly follow Nai.

36:21.080 --> 36:25.080
But Nai, are you that confident
we won't get poached?

36:27.680 --> 36:31.120
Whoever can successfully poach you guys
will also be able to poach me.

36:34.040 --> 36:36.200
I'm quite touched to hear you say that.

36:38.280 --> 36:42.640
Interested in battling? Whoever wins
gets first dibs on the office.

36:45.720 --> 36:48.000
I knew that warm feeling was an illusion!

37:01.760 --> 37:04.840
These are 12th grade math problems.
I can't believe you got them all right!

37:06.080 --> 37:06.920
Wish.

37:08.800 --> 37:11.840
You already knew
I'd have to fulfill your wish,

37:11.920 --> 37:13.520
before you even asked, right?

37:14.080 --> 37:15.480
Go ahead. What's your wish?

37:16.720 --> 37:19.600
I see that you brought your laptop today.

37:22.280 --> 37:25.520
Yes, I did some homework
at the library, before I came over.

37:26.040 --> 37:28.400
So, I want to watch you play your game.

37:28.920 --> 37:32.200
No. According to our agreement,

37:32.440 --> 37:34.760
today is not your gaming time.

37:35.080 --> 37:38.920
That's the overall principle.
We can't break the rule. Change your wish.

37:39.360 --> 37:43.040
Then... I'll use
next week's gaming time today.

37:47.000 --> 37:47.840
No exceptions next time.

38:00.200 --> 38:03.600
Swordswoman in red!
Ms. Weiwei, you're so cool!

38:05.920 --> 38:06.800
Someone's calling for you.

38:07.200 --> 38:09.920
Yixiao Naihe says,
"Weiwei, come kill monsters."

38:11.120 --> 38:12.120
Who's this Yixiao Naihe?

38:13.240 --> 38:14.280
My friend from the game.

38:19.760 --> 38:20.880
So many people here!

38:21.520 --> 38:25.640
But there are already a few Xiaoyus
fighting the monster.

38:27.080 --> 38:28.400
Xiaoyang, you're in luck.

38:29.000 --> 38:32.280
You get to witness my first-ever attempt
at stealing prey from someone.

38:33.600 --> 38:36.080
Isn't stealing prey a bad thing?

38:36.800 --> 38:38.960
It is, indeed. Don't do that.

38:39.360 --> 38:41.040
But this Xiaoyu Qingqing

38:41.120 --> 38:44.200
tried to falsely accuse me
of stealing their prey the other day.

38:44.880 --> 38:47.560
They refused to admit it, when exposed.
What do you think I should do?

38:47.920 --> 38:49.880
Steal prey from her a hundred times.

38:49.960 --> 38:51.960
I support you, Ms. Weiwei.

38:52.920 --> 38:54.640
Look! They've run off!

39:01.120 --> 39:04.440
It fell down. Go pick up the chest
and see what's inside!

39:07.000 --> 39:09.480
Rare material, diamond.

39:10.200 --> 39:11.280
Is it serious stuff?

39:12.560 --> 39:15.520
The system made a public announcement.
What do you think?

39:17.680 --> 39:20.680
Ms. Weiwei, this game is so much fun!

39:20.760 --> 39:22.760
Can I play for a while?

39:25.040 --> 39:27.600
Was this your plan all along?

39:29.360 --> 39:30.800
Fine. Just a little while.

39:31.160 --> 39:33.720
I'll ask my friend to show you around.

39:37.200 --> 39:39.120
Let me. You can tend to other things.

39:39.200 --> 39:42.000
- Sure. Thanks.
- You're welcome.

39:45.880 --> 39:48.160
It's amazing, Ms. Weiwei!

39:48.640 --> 39:52.360
Yixiao Naihe is incredible at battling.
I can't beat him.

39:53.840 --> 39:56.560
Tell him you're a kid,
and ask him to give you a break.

39:58.360 --> 40:00.600
No way! I'm a man.

40:00.680 --> 40:02.680
I must battle with my own strength.

40:09.040 --> 40:13.680
Ms. Weiwei, people are slamming you,
accusing you of stealing a prey.

40:13.760 --> 40:17.240
Xiaoyu Qingqing, who framed you last time,
is playing the victim in the chat room.

40:18.160 --> 40:20.720
She says you bully weak girls
like her team.

40:23.280 --> 40:24.920
They want you to hand over the diamond.

40:25.440 --> 40:27.960
Ms. Weiwei, come take a look!

40:29.200 --> 40:30.240
Wait, I'll be right over.

40:35.840 --> 40:36.840
Let's see.

40:40.480 --> 40:43.320
Look, Ms. Weiwei, this player says,

40:43.400 --> 40:45.720
Xiaoyu Qingqing and her team
tried to steal the prey.

40:45.800 --> 40:48.280
You only stood up for them.

40:50.560 --> 40:52.440
Xiaoyu Qingqing doesn't admit it.

40:53.640 --> 40:56.800
Look, Ms. Weiwei!
This player posted a video.

40:58.720 --> 41:02.640
Fantastic! That shut up the Xiaoyus.

41:02.720 --> 41:05.320
No one in the public chat room
can smear you anymore.

41:06.600 --> 41:07.720
Be low-key.

41:09.480 --> 41:12.520
Xiaoyu Qingqing is so good at
playing the victim.

41:13.160 --> 41:15.720
Two can play at this game. Watch me.

41:17.680 --> 41:20.320
I've never said much.

41:20.920 --> 41:23.720
I always thought,
a clean hand wants no washing.

41:24.920 --> 41:29.440
But I suddenly feel very discouraged,
after getting universally condemned.

41:31.200 --> 41:32.880
How's that? It breaks your heart, no?

41:37.520 --> 41:40.320
Nice. You're skilled at playing innocent.

41:44.840 --> 41:48.000
I'm offering high prices for diamonds.

41:50.840 --> 41:52.800
Nai is speaking in the public chat room?

41:54.360 --> 41:56.440
- I want a photo with you.
- I want an autograph!

41:57.200 --> 42:01.040
Yixiao, do you want diamonds
to enhance weapon properties?

42:02.720 --> 42:03.800
Nope.

42:04.840 --> 42:05.880
Then why buy diamonds?

42:07.160 --> 42:09.400
So my wife can play with it.

42:17.360 --> 42:19.320
Are you happy, Mrs. Nai?

42:19.400 --> 42:22.280
Xiaoyu Qingqing must be fuming right now.

42:25.560 --> 42:28.760
Yes, I'm happy. By the way,
"Jiushi Buchifan"

42:28.840 --> 42:31.320
must be one of you guys' subaccount?
It can't be a coincidence.

42:31.400 --> 42:34.520
Just when I went to steal their prey,
that subaccount started recording.

42:36.680 --> 42:37.760
It belongs to Yugong and the others.

42:39.800 --> 42:43.880
We got three subaccounts, specifically
to steal prey from Xiaoyu Qingqing.

42:43.960 --> 42:46.600
We stole prey from her three times.
She finally offed us.

42:47.720 --> 42:48.840
You should praise us.

42:49.960 --> 42:51.960
Insidious! So insidious!

42:54.640 --> 42:59.320
It's not us! Nai put us up to it.

43:02.800 --> 43:04.080
Naihe is so clever!

43:07.000 --> 43:12.000
What? Differential treatment!
I'm done!

45:45.600 --> 45:48.040
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
